high_descs: Walk straight to the wall, turn left to the stove, and turn right to the sink.
Pick up the yellow knife from the sink.
Cut the apple in the sink into three pieces.
Place the knife in the sink.
Pick up a slice of apple from the sink.
Turn left to face the microwave.
Place the apple on the plate in the microwave, heat it up, and take apple back out.
Turn left and walk towards the counter.
Place the apple piece to the right of the yellow knife on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Place a cooked slice of apple to the right of the yellow knife on the counter.

high_descs: Go forward, turn to your left and then turn right so that you are facing the sink
Pick up the knife from the sink
Slice the apple that is in the sink
Put the knife back in to the sink
Pick up a chunk of apple
Turn to face your left
Put the piece of apple in the microwave and cook it for a few seconds, before taking it back out
Walk to your left and face the counter top
Set the piece of apple down on the counter top
anns.task_desc: Slice an apple, cook it and set it on the counter

high_descs: Go straight towards the fridge, then make a left at the refrigerator, walk to the center of the kitchen and turn to the sink at your right.
Pick up the knife in the sink.
Cut the apple in the sink into slices.
Place the knife back into the sink.
Pick up an apple slice from the sink.
Turn to the microwave, on your left.
Place the apple slice in the microwave, heat it up, then remove the apple from the microwave.
Turn to your left and walk to the counter.
Place the apple slice on the counter, between the knife and the ladle.
anns.task_desc: Put a warm apple slice on the counter.
